CustomField.description: Allows Enabling/Disabling a subscription. Determines if outbox records are created at the time the Message is inserted. Outbox records that are already created will still attempt to send.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Allows Enabling/Disabling a subscription. Determines if outbox records are created at the time the Message is inserted. Outbox records that are already created will still attempt to send.
CustomField.label: Enabled
